SUMMARY:Tri-Co Quizzo at Top Tomato in Philly
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['College Advancement']\\nCategory: Meeting\\nThe
  tradition continues: Tri-Co Quizzo is back! Join alums from all three of 
 the Tri-Co colleges once again for a battle of wits and memories! Defend t
 he honor of your alma mater\, put your storehouse of arcane and sometimes 
 useful information to the test\, and enjoy a fun evening out. Top Tomato B
 ar & Pizza116 S 11th StPhiladelphia\, PA 19107 Event DetailsThe cost is $1
 0 per person\, which includes a coupon for one free drink (up to $6 – or
  $6 off any more expensive drink). Come as a pre-formed team (of up to six
  people)\, or partner up when you arrive. Please RSVPRegistration is limit
 ed to 25 people from each college. We’ll accept RSVPs until Thursday\, M
 arch 5 or until the event reaches capacity\, whichever comes first. Regist
 er early\; this event tends to fill up and there will not be a waitlist. 
   \\nDetails: https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Deven
 t%26eventid%3D1364155661
URL:https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%
 3D1364155661
CATEGORIES:Meeting
END:VEVENT
