SUMMARY:Portland Book Club
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['College Advancement']\\nCategory: Meeting\\nThe
  next SwatPDX book club is 7-9pm on March 12\, 2026. The book selection is
  The Left Hand of Darkness by Portland's own Ursula K. Le Guin. It will be
  held at an alum's home in Portland (the street address will be sent to fo
 lks who register a few days before the meeting). Hope to see you there!  
 Please RSVP for the book club by Sunday\, March 5. There’s an area of th
 e form to indicate interest in future book club meetings and be included i
 n communications about other SwatPDX events\, even if you won’t be atten
 ding the March book club meeting. Hope to see you on March 12! Sincerely\,
  Ana Cragnolino ’93\, Catherine Rose ’97\, and Becky Voorheis ’93Swa
 tPDX co-leads\\nDetails: https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=v
 iew%3Devent%26eventid%3D1368438079
URL:https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%
 3D1368438079
CATEGORIES:Meeting
END:VEVENT
