DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['GSC'\, 'Be Well'\, 'Sexual Health Advocates'\, 
 'SWELL Team'\, 'Worth Health Center']\\nCategory: Meeting\\nJoin us for a 
 celebration of bodily autonomy and an expression of resistance to recent p
 olicy attacks on our bodies through education\, joy\, camaraderie\, and ad
 dressing our basic needs. There will be FREE Menstrual pain simulator expe
 rienceMenstrual cups and period productsSafer sex productsGender Affirming
  HaircutsAppointments for the Gender Affirmation Closet (binders\, packers
 \, trans tape\, and more!)Clothing Swap& more!Additionally\, there will be
  a prize raffle including menstrual products\, pride merch\, gender affirm
 ing garments\, and sex toys! Several on-campus offices and off-campus orga
 nizations will be tabling on gender affirmation\, pregnancy\, abortion\, m
 enstrual health\, reusable period products\, and healthy sex and relations
 hips.\\nDetails: https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Dev
 ent%26eventid%3D1362038296
