SUMMARY:SSQL Workshop: Intro to R and R Studio
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['Sociology and Anthropology'\, 'Economics'\, 'Po
 litical Science']\\nCategory: Training/Workshop\\nR is a powerful tool for
  social science data  analysis. This hands-on workshop will introduce you
  to opening and manipulating data\, working with data structures and varia
 ble types and conduct descriptive analyses of real datasets. We’ll also 
 cover strategies for handling common errors and provide a brief introducti
 on to R Markdown for reproducible reports.\\nDetails: https://swatcentral.
 swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%3D1357216277
