 ance\, while connecting minds\, bodies\, and spirits. The class incorporat
 es cardio\, flexibility\, strength\, and balance while staying playful and
  listening to some favorite songs. All levels of ability and experience ar
 e welcome! \\nDetails: https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=vi
 ew%3Devent%26eventid%3D1342628517
