 ndy Hines welcome you to drop in\, say hello\, and learn more about what w
 e’re up to at our weekly open office hours on Wednesdays from 1-2pm in P
 arrish W201. Tea\, coffee\, and snacks will be available too! Check out th
 e Get Involved page\, Publications\, and the rest of the Aydelotte Foundat
 ion website to learn more about some of the things we've been working on. 
 If you can’t make it to office hours and would like to meet\, feel free 
 to reach out to us for an appointment at another time.\\nDetails: https://
