SUMMARY:Garnet Day
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ["President's Office"]\\nCategory: Reception\\nGu
 ess to win big this Garnet Day!    Stop by the Kohlberg Coffee Bar any t
 ime between 9 a.m. and 4 p.m. to guess how many pieces of candy are in the
  Garnet Day candy jar. The correct guess (or the closest without going ove
 r) wins a $200 gift certificate to the Broad Table Tavern\, compliments of
  the Inn at Swarthmore. Second prize is a $75 gift certificate to the Broa
 d Table Tavern. Third prize is the jar of candy.      Garnet Day Guess
 ing Game Kohlberg Coffee Bar Thursday\, March 9 9 – 4 p.m. Winners will 
 be notified individually the week of March 16 Get Out the Vote will be on 
 hand to share important resources.  As always\, remember to wear your Col
 lege gear to show your Swarthmore spirit!\\nDetails: https://swatcentral.s
 warthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=view%3Devent%26eventid%3D1281162993
