DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['Swarthmore College Libraries'\, 'McCabe Library
 ']\\nCategory: Poster Session\\nThe 2025/26 cohort of student UX Interns p
 resent posters on their independent projects\, which include (but are not 
 limited to!) user studies of library spaces and websites\, the Shuttle app
