SUMMARY:Mindfulness and Meditation
DESCRIPTION:Organized by: ['Be Well'\, 'Worth Health Center']\\nCategory: T
 raining/Workshop\\nCome to the weekly mindfulness and meditation gathering
 \, a place to reconnect\, distress\, relax in a community\, and learn conc
 rete tools of mindful awareness. Each week\, the group will explore a diff
 erent practice that can easily integrate into your day-to-day life.\\nDeta
